  "technicalDetails": "<p><u>Features:</u></p><ul><li>Firearm Blueprint</li><li>Firearm Variations (Rifle, Pistol, Shotgun)</li><li>Target Dummy</li><li>Reserves Component (Stores Ammunition)</li><li>Basic FPS Movement Component</li><li>Gym and Demo Level</li><li>Firearm Meshes and Animations (Imported from Lyra)</li><li>VFX: Bullet Tracer, Muzzle Flash, Bullet Impact</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Number of Blueprints: 17</p><p>Input: Mouse and Keyboard</p><p>Network Replicated: No</p><p>Supported Development Platforms: Windows, Mac</p><p>Documentation: Online Documentation</p><p>Additional Notes: Make sure to check out the support <a href=\"https://discord.gg/gpXES5cujp\" rel=\"nofollow\">discord server</a> if you have any suggestions, feedback, or encounter any issues with the pack.</p>",
